title: Inventories of Principal Items Bought for Production and Resale, Per Cent Reporting Larger Inventories for United States
notes:
Data Represent The Percentage Reporting Higher Inventories Plus One Half Of A Per Cent Reporting "No Change." Source: Purchasing Agents Association Of Chicago, Combined Statistical And Analytical Report Of The Business Survey Committee, Monthly Releases Sent By V. Zarnowitz.

This NBER data series m05136 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 5 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter05.html.
